        <property propertyId="38f94dd1-d5aa-41b8-b182-c0c42985d9dc" amount="0.035648217" unitId="7b75baf0-cbee-45e6-bf66-af119da06553">
          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Estimated value.  This price is approximated by the price calculated based on a specific designs of compression refrigeration processes by Luyben, W. L (2017). The compression refrigeration processes allows investiating detailed operating conditions and calculating economic costs (capital investment and energy cost). This refrigeration price depends on the cryogenic temperature level and represents  the energy removed from the cryogenic process with 1 MW capacity. Exchange rates of 0.8865 EURO2017/USD2017 and 0.83 EURO2005/EURO2017 were used.

References:
Luyben, William L. "Estimating refrigeration costs at cryogenic temperatures." Computers &amp; Chemical Engineering 103 (2017): 144-150.</comment>
        </property>
